Class MBeanGlassfishRuntimeServices

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.services.RuntimeServices
      • org.eclipse.persistence.services.glassfish.GlassfishRuntimeServices
        • org.eclipse.persistence.services.glassfish.MBeanGlassfishRuntimeServices
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MBeanGlassfishRuntimeServicesMBean, MBeanRuntimeServicesMBean
    public class MBeanGlassfishRuntimeServices
extends GlassfishRuntimeServices
implements MBeanGlassfishRuntimeServicesMBean

    Purpose: Provide a dynamic interface into the EclipseLink Session.

    Description: This class is meant to provide a framework for gaining access to configuration of the EclipseLink Session during runtime. It will provide the basis for development of a JMX service and possibly other frameworks.

    Since:
    EclipseLink 2.1.1
